# Onboarding Guide

Welcome to the team! This guide will help you get started.

N> Make sure you have your laptop set up before your first day.
N> Contact IT at support@example.com if you need help.

## First Day Checklist

- [x] Pick up badge from reception
- [x] Complete HR paperwork
- [ ] Set up development environment
- [ ] Join team Slack channels

T> Use the `setup.sh` script to automate most of the environment setup.

## Important Policies

W> All code must be reviewed by at least two team members before merging.

!> Never commit secrets or API keys to the repository.
!> Use the vault service for all sensitive configuration.

